# ─── Line ending normalisation ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: normalise to LF in the repo, native on checkout for source files.
* text=auto

# ─── Test fixtures ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Fixture files MUST stay byte-for-byte identical across platforms.
# Git's autocrlf/eol conversion would change content hashes and break tests.
tests/fixtures/** -text

# ─── Binary assets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png  binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.mp4  binary
*.exe  binary
*.lnk  binary
